Class TM

  • java.lang.Object
    • TM

  • public class TM
extends java.lang.Object
    A ticket machine, inspired by the "naive ticket machine project", but much more complex Features: 1. Price is determined by customer's "agegroup" 2. Only sensible values are allowed into fields (e.g. no negative money/balance) 3. A password-protected "technician" method that can change instance variables (not available in a session)
